description: a(n) = least value such that sequence increases and pairwise differences are unique.
comments: A variation on A005282 (Mian-Chowla, where positive differences of pairs of elements are unique) by starting with a(1) = 1, a(2) = 5.
author: Gerald A. Mischke (Gerald.Mischke(AT)mutualofomaha.com), Dec 13 2000
